Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  给人添麻烦也要适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们如果不是堂岛先生的外甥和他的朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就不是警告一下就能了事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  里中？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天城？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说她直到昨天傍晚为止都还在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之后谁都没有再看到过雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实天城雪子的家人已经提交了寻人申请
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是雪子小姐的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们有想到什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说雪子小姐看起来很痛苦之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的受害人山野女主播  案发前住在天城屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是投诉似乎蜂拥而至
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果老板娘因为压力过大而倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后雪子小姐正好是老板娘的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局里也有人说她因为有着见不得人的理由而躲起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思啊  你想说雪子是犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  这终究只是谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子怎么可能是犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这谣言又不是我传出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  里中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  雪子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须去救雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天午夜电视里出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中你最好还是在外面等我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去  我绝对要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要一说出口  就再也不听劝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  天城就在这里面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊的鼻子都能清楚地闻到呢熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要一个人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你没办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下熊熊啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  完全没有在意周围的情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是老师啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳介还需要继续努力啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我就直呼其名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…雪子的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「红色真合适你呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讨厌雪子这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪什么的  冰冷且转眼间就会消融
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是虚无缥缈的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}但是  却和我非常相称啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子…你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}和除了继承旅馆之外毫无价值的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里啊  回答我啊  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只有千枝这么对我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  红色真适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有千枝给予了我生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝既开朗又坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且什么都会做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所没有的东西  她全都拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种  我这种人和千枝比起来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝会保护我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善解人意的千枝会保护这个毫无价值的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善解人意的千枝什么的  真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？  是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里中千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在说什么啊  我才是里中千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是里中千枝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  那个雪子居然说她被我保护着？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说自己毫无价值  不这样怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子是个美女  皮肤又白  还很有女人味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都被男生们捧在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的雪子时不时会用自卑的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉真是让人爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子其实是个离开了我就什么都做不到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的地位  我的地位显然要比她高得多不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  里中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不对  这根本不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么数量啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样  装作没看见不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快来镇住我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口  你这种家伙  你这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种家伙才不是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾即为影  是为真实的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你也要来碍事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让你吃点苦头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你太帅了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还存在着啊？  快点给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我会负责照顾雪子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为垫脚石来照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垫脚…石？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人的话就什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我才是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但雪子却依靠着这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雪子是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里…中  不要被迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么迷惑不迷惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心…话！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子是个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被男人们追捧着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这就是你内心深处的真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑陋的嫉妒之心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明离开了我就什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是全都在依赖着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是  我的  真心话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心话？  这不也挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  你们也是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  我们是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我内心深处的另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一直都不敢面对的  无可救药的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我就是我  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你想认同并接受我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我就这样把你撕成碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳阳阳阳介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从羁绊中获得了新的Arcana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够使用多个Persona的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「Wild」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——被选中之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选中…之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Change
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(320,327)}Jack O'Lantern
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克南瓜灯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  能使用两种Persona吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如果这边下起雾的话  雪子说不定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的身体却不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拯救天城的话  里中的力量一定是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为谢礼  我就破例让你看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被养在我家里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长的胖乎乎的  而且还非常臭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  正是这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我邂逅了我最好的朋友雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:08.43,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c000000}人之间的羁绊就是真正的力量
Comment: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:18.09,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}下条线索
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.53,0:24:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要挡路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够了那种烦人的束缚了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.89,0:24:31.44,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}下集  非此处的某处


